reviewText: The disk didn't play. My daughter was very unhappy.

WARNING! This is a Region 2 dvd meaning you will need a compatible dvd player for it to work. I wish this had been clearer in the description. As I did not wish to purchase a new dvd player, I returned the item to Great Britain and had to file an A to Z claim with Amazon, who ultimately credited me for the item. I was still out the $17.95 for return shipping though. I learned my lesson the hard way. You've been warned!!
Came ahead of schedule I know my wife will love it!
Nobody mentioned it was from the UK and wouldn't play with my DVD player
The DVDs did not work. When I entered the DVD in the DVD player, an error message appears.  I am waiting to hear back from them if they will accept my return and refund me my money.
We ordered this, 2 of the movies worked once, then went to play them again and they didn't work.  One of them didn't work at all.
Pissed. The damn movies don't work.  This was a Christmas present and it's not even any good.  Just wonderful.
